          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 mt-12">
              <button class="h-11 w-52 px-1 py-2.5 rounded-[25px] border-2 border-[#6a2831] justify-center items-center gap-3.5 inline-flex"> <a class="text-center text-[#6a2831] text-xl font-semibold font-['Montserrat']" href="">Read More</a></button>
